{"tid":2307638,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[研究] 香港有無可能出現一個新嘅新聞媒體","createTime":"2020-12-01T09:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T13:51:32.000Z","uid":35070,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1af58a2b7ad82c7b6d61fe377f114df520dd2a6","tid":2307638,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:45:56.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">前言</span></strong></ins><br />\n面對住香港舊有傳統媒體自我審查、亂報及政治正確情況下, 香港媒體已經禮崩樂壞, 相信將來都唔會好得去邊。<br />\n面對住呢種情況, 係應該去研究一下將來有無可能出現一個新嘅新聞媒體?<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">例子: Newsmax</span></strong></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/coMLaJqPtSxbp8vu8jobnb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net%2FcoMLaJqPtSxbp8vu8jobnb.jpg&h=e018826b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNewsmax, 美國保守派新聞媒體, 由Christopher Ruddy喺1998年創立, 總部位於美國佛羅里達州東南部西棕櫚灘 (West Palm Beach)。<br />\n<br />\n呢個台嘅崛起係喺今年美國總統大選, 大部分美國人不滿傳統電視台腰斬Trump記者會之後, 再加埋Trump 都覺得 Fox呢類傳統右媒都唔夠右, 好多佢嘅Fans都轉晒去睇Newsmax TV, 仲搞到傳統電視台收視一路咁跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/125114746_10223802448913276_5797114716286453791_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=mudtuX4d11oAX94ncoY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=9e6369fe38d9750cb7ecc07911f16c6c&amp;oe=5FEAB7F6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F125114746_10223802448913276_5797114716286453791_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DmudtuX4d11oAX94ncoY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3D9e6369fe38d9750cb7ecc07911f16c6c%26oe%3D5FEAB7F6&h=2794567c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n收視率由原本只有2.5萬人, 大幅上升到有43.7萬人睇緊, 之後仲搞到Fox股價跌成7%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7d62d4a19b3f950e6ab85b7d6bf0e715230e32","tid":2307638,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-